Progression line for Magelife

1. Harvest Gravel, plant fibers and sticks.
	Knap flint against stone
	Make flint hatchet
	Harvest Logs with hatchet
	Make chopping block
	Cut logs into Planks on Chopping Block
	Craft Better flint tools
	Make a Millstone and Handcrank for further progression into other areas

	Mine Copper Ore and Tin Ore
	Using a normal furnace smelt copper into ingots

	Level up your mining skill to eventually mine Iron and unlock the next skill tree


	